{"type": "article", "id": 46464, "title": "巧克力不缺噱头，这一次是吃掉行星表面｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-10-24T23:15:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23747, "name": "一融设计"}, {"id": 44971, "name": "Neomam Studios"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 232, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171024171453WYdgzSHk0K6DhBwl.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p11 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Chocolat The [Planet] by Rong Design</h3><p>巧克力的噱头总是不嫌多。既然<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/45387.html\">城市地图</a>能做成巧克力，星球为什么不行？<a href=\"http://www.rong-design.com/index.php?id=1820\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chocolat The [Planet]</a> 是<a href=\"http://www.rong-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">一融设计</a>与巧克力品牌 AMENO 共同打造的实验性项目，三款巧克力分别被制作成了地球、月亮和火星的表面。值得一提的是，它的外包装也很贴题地采用了圆形镂空，内部印刷着来自 NASA 的相片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171515QYoHaO6n0xKE27tV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171515gfmW5esku7824H3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171515qm2NPcK4ZE7k8Xwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.426042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171515vlp5F8RNiqatIm3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TEAMOSA</h3><p>台湾初创团队 TEAMOSA 的两位创始人来自一个“茶叶世家”，他们的家族据称已经经营了 34 年的茶叶生意。以推广茶文化为初衷，他们开发了一款同名的胶囊泡茶机。泡茶机具备两种冲泡方式：直接使用胶囊或者将茶叶倒进顶部的槽内。用户可以通过配套的 App，对泡茶时的各种参数进行精准的调控，例如水温和浓淡。它还拥有自动清洗残渣的功能，只要在泡完茶叶之后轻触前方按键即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/teamosa/teamosa-your-personal-tea-brewing-master\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 259 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171529JiynMCkoOUZQevAD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783824\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171529BtqRnaw4XFUNWr8m.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171530nUoWL1Yl6EuJPAXx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171528EadK9It07h3rYRUp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651471\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Circular Power Strip by Urban Outfitters</h3><p>电子设备多需要一起充电时，传统的长方形接线板可能就没那么好用了：插座不够用或是空间不足导致两个插头“争地盘”都是很常见的烦恼。美国零售品牌 Urban Outfitters 为此推出了一款圆盘状的接线板，增大的间距和放置在中间的开关键使整个布局看起来清爽了许多。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.urbanoutfitters.com/shop/uo_tune_in-circular-power-strip\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价为 39 美元，分为浅橙和浅绿两种颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171547W9fhqaYmoudiGpLS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171547xbsLX3wfhBNSpg54.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171547DpPSgkXYh9OsynGd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171547aGqoIh2PNDybn48Q.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710241715474Ik0bFDwSlEtBhp7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Magnetic Clock Blackhole by Josselin Zaïgouche</h3><p>以经典科幻电影《2001：太空漫游》为灵感，法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.bozastudio.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Josselin Zaïgouche</a> 设计了一款迷你版的巨石碑时钟。象征三根指针的小球借助磁力吸引，沿着时钟表面的涟漪移动。通过这种颇具诗意的表达时间的方式，Zaïgouche 希望能够让人们在忙碌的工作之余能够感受到一丝平静。目前，它还只是一款概念产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171605NKwXDxlS2OzgZp7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171606i0JaMvxIBjClA53z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171605GRAteV0Zw9W7SqgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.876190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Homeadvisor by Neomam Studios</h3><p>你有没有想过根据某位导演的风格去改造自己的卧室？最近，英国品牌咨询公司 <a href=\"http://neomam.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Neomam Studios</a> 为美国房地产网站 <a href=\"https://www.homeadvisor.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HomeAdvisor</a> 设计了 7 套风格各异的<a href=\"https://www.homeadvisor.com/r/if-film-directors-designed-your-bedroom/\" rel=\"nofollow\">卧室概念图</a>：主要使用棕色和绿色的乡村风来源于彼得·杰克逊执导的“魔戒三部曲”中霍比特人居住的夏尔镇，宛如在云端、充满冒险气质的儿童房则参考了宫崎骏导演的动画片，看起来有些阴森的黑暗系则是借鉴了蒂姆·波顿的奇幻世界。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171617xPJNH9gL8RkfmvId.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.965770\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171616C6gWlvUyhzMqIe4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.966993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171617mxuIWaGNkXqOUVF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.960880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171617fqKxGPYA58IhEMzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>36days Electronics by Vinicius Araújo</h3><p>出于对字体 Helvetica 的喜爱，巴西设计师 Vinicius Araújo 最近完成了一组有趣的字体设计作品：他选择了 26 个品牌，然后将品牌首字母和旗下的标志性产品组合在一起。如果你对自己识别这些产品有信心的话，可以通过他的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/57705665/36days-Electronics\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bechance</a> 页面做个测试。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171806HRkJQoZwCIYfbljS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.358333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171806yP8W9l2TX3RIc5tQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171024171806GXpY4U1WZ6ry8ixN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}